data.description: Welcome Home! You've found this gem of a property here in Pflugerville, TX! Residing in the sought out for neighborhood of Highland Park North. This home boasts a spacious 2982 sqft, has 5 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms & has an in-ground POOL to beat the 100+ degree heat here in TX! Enjoy your mornings/evenings on your covered front or back porch or pool deck! As you walk in, this beautiful open concept home has fantastic wood styled ceramic tile floors throughout the main living area and kitchen, with carpets in all bedrooms. Front room can be used as a 5th bedroom or even home office. Solid countertops in kitchen, recess lighting and a walk in pantry with beautiful glass door. Kitchen overlooks the dining, living and breakfast area, perfect for entertaining & those special occasions! Wine/Prep Room available as well for those wine lovers! Large living area accompanied by the fireplace with stone tiling coverage, makes for a cozy spot to relax. Primary bathroom has dual vanity, garden tub/walk-in shower split, and huge walk in closet. Home has a full sized garage with plenty space for some storage as well, also has an 8x10 storage in the backyard. 5" Gutters around home. Roof is less than a year old, AC is 2-3 years old, Recent paint, water heater 2 years old. Close proximity to entertainment and shopping centers, Amazon, Round Rock, Premier HS & Highland Park Elementary. Home is primed and priced to sell, bring your buyers and offers!
